          "GroupsPage.jsx lines 107-108: 'console.warn('Failed to save config:', err)' \u2014 same pattern for save/delete/rename config operations",
          "GroupManager.jsx line 256-258: handleSave properly shows formError on failure \u2014 the right approach",
