        "evidence": [
          "AccountsBreakdown.jsx line 80: 'function AccountSection({ label, total, totalColor, pieData, groups, colors, pieHeight, pieInnerRadius, pieOuterRadius })' \u2014 9 destructured props",
          "Three of these (pieHeight, pieInnerRadius, pieOuterRadius) are always passed together and always derived from isMobile \u2014 they are a cohesive group"
